Review
Moving beyond energy homeostasis: New roles for glucagon-like
peptide-1 in food and drug reward
India A. Reddy a,b,c,e,⇑, Gregg D. Stanwood a,d, Aurelio Galli a,c,e,⇑
a Vanderbilt Brain Institute, Vanderbilt University Medical Center, Nashville, TN, USA
b Neuroscience Graduate Program, Vanderbilt University Medical Center, Nashville, TN, USA
c Neuroscience Program in Substance Abuse, Vanderbilt University Medical Center, Nashville, TN, USA
d Department of Pharmacology, Vanderbilt University Medical Center, Nashville, TN, USA
e Department of Molecular Physiology and Biophysics, Vanderbilt University Medical Center, Nashville, TN, USA
a r t i c l e
i n f o
Article history:
Available online xxxx
Keywords:
Glucagon-like peptide-1
Reward
